# Backlog
### User Stories
1. As a new player I want to create a new account so I can play with my own unique username. :)
2. As a returning player I want to login so I can play. :)
3. As a player I want to create a character with a unique name I create. :)
4. As a player I want to have a variety of different background and font themes so I can pick one that lets me play the most comfortably. :)
5. (1) As a player I would like to type my commands into the text box and submit it with "ENTER". :)
--Switch for commands
--List of Commands

6. As a player I would like to click on the directions I want to go so I don't have to type it every time. :) 
7. (3) As a player I would like to see what current actions I have available to me so I can strategically decide what to do next. :) 
--help list
--adaptive
8. (4) As a player I would like to view my current inventory so I know what I have and what I might need. :)
--items
--view
-- add items 
9. As a player I would like to click the red search button to search the room so I don't have to type it. :)
10. As a player I want to see my previous actions and events so I know if I made a wrong move.  :)
11. As a player I want to be able to drop inventory items so I can make room for better stuff. :|
12. As a player I want to read the description of the area I'm currently in so I know what might be there.:)
13. As a player I want to take items I find after searching an area so I can have a better chance at survival.  :|
14. As a player I want to see when an event is triggered so I can know what is occurring. :)
15. As a player I want to see when an event is triggered so I know I have to act quickly to survive.
16. As a player I would like to monitor my health so I know when to use a med kit. :)
17. As a player I want to view my current level so I know how much progress I made. :) 
18. As a player I want to view how close to leveling up I am so I know how much it will take to level up.:)
19. As a player I want to see the level of a weapon so I know if I can use it. :)
20. (2) As a player I would like to attack so I can kill before I get killed. :|
--Enemies
--add to switch
--health
--damage
21. As a player I would like to defend so I can reduce the amount of damage done to me. :(
22. As a player I want to see how many times I died and survived so I can compare my performance to my friends. :)
23. As a player I would like to equip different gear I find around the world so I can improve my survivability. :|
24. As a player I would like to replay the same scenario I just died in to see if I can fix my mistakes
25. As a player I want to use items in my inventory so I can use their effects. :|
26. As a player I want to increase different attributes so I can customize my character to my play style. :)
27. As a player I would like to see what room Iâ€™m currently in, in relation to the world I have explored.
28. As a player I want to load my last saved game so I can continue.
29. As a player I want to break down a door so I don't have to go looking for a key that might not exist.
30. As a player I want to adjust the relativity marks to my liking.
31. As a player I want to adjust the different sounds to my liking.
32. As a player I would like to save my game and come back when I'm free again.
